trailingComments.value: * * Repeatedly yields the same deque that is updated to contain the current * element of the input iterable iterator and the next n-1 * elements of the input iterable iterator. * * @example * window( 2, range( 100 ) ) ; * // is equivalent to * zip( range( 100 ) , range( 1 , 100 ) ) ; * * @param {number} n - The window size. * @param {IterableIterator} iterable - The input iterable. * @returns {IterableIterator}
